<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>The Convergence Codex — Al-Mahdi & The Antichrist</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cinzel+Decorative:wght@400;700;900&family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;0,600;1,300;1,400&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --gold: #c9a84c;
    --gold-light: #e8cc7a;
    --gold-dim: #8a6d2f;
    --obsidian: #0d0d0f;
    --deep: #111218;
    --mid: #1a1b24;
    --surface: #20222e;
    --border: #2a2d3e;
    --text: #d4cfc6;
    --text-dim: #888299;
    --islamic-green: #2d6e4e;
    --islamic-green-light: #4aab7a;
    --biblical-blue: #1e3a6b;
    --biblical-blue-light: #4a7cc7;
    --secular-purple: #4a1e6b;
    --secular-purple-light: #9a4acc;
    --danger: #c94c4c;
    --agree: #4cc97a;
  }

  * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--obsidian);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ── HERO ─────────────────────────────── */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 60px 40px;
    position: relative;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 50%, rgba(201,168,76,0.06) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 50%, rgba(201,168,76,0.04) 0%, transparent 60%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #0d0d0f 0%, #111218 100%);
  }

  .hero::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent, transparent 80px, rgba(201,168,76,0.03) 80px, rgba(201,168,76,0.03) 81px),
      repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, transparent 80px, rgba(201,168,76,0.03) 80px, rgba(201,168,76,0.03) 81px);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-emblem {
    font-size: 80px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    animation: pulse 4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 0.8; transform: scale(1); }
    50% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.05); }
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif;
    font-size: clamp(28px, 5vw, 64px);
    font-weight: 900;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    line-height: 1.2;
    text-shadow: 0 0 60px rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .hero-sub {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: clamp(16px, 2vw, 22px);
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-style: italic;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .thesis-box {
    max-width: 700px;
    border: 1px solid var(--gold-dim);
    padding: 28px 36px;
    background: rgba(201,168,76,0.05);
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }

  .thesis-box::before {
    content: 'CENTRAL THESIS';
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    left: 30px;
    background: var(--obsidian);
    padding: 0 12px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 3px;
  }

  .thesis-box p {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .nav-pills {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .nav-pill {
    padding: 10px 24px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--surface);
    color: var(--text-dim);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    transition: all 0.3s;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .nav-pill:hover {
    border-color: var(--gold);
    color: var(--gold);
    background: rgba(201,168,76,0.08);
  }

  /* ── SECTION LAYOUT ────────────────────── */
  section {
    padding: 80px 40px;
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .section-tag {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 4px;
    color: var(--gold-dim);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    display: block;
  }

  .section-header h2 {
    font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif;
    font-size: clamp(22px, 3vw, 40px);
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .section-header p {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .divider {
    width: 100%;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold-dim), transparent);
    margin: 80px 0;
  }

  /* ── BEGINNER ORIENTATION ──────────────── */
  .orientation-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 28px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .orientation-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 30px;
    background: rgba(32,34,46,0.45);
    position: relative;
  }

  .orientation-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 3px;
  }

  .orientation-card.biblical::before { background: var(--biblical-blue-light); }
  .orientation-card.islamic::before { background: var(--islamic-green-light); }

  .orientation-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .orientation-card.biblical h3 { color: var(--biblical-blue-light); }
  .orientation-card.islamic h3 { color: var(--islamic-green-light); }

  .orientation-card p {
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }

  .orientation-card strong {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .role-map {
    margin-top: 36px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: rgba(13,13,15,0.35);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .role-map-header {
    padding: 16px 20px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .role-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(150px, 0.8fr) minmax(220px, 1.2fr) minmax(220px, 1.2fr) minmax(220px, 1.4fr);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(42,45,62,0.55);
  }

  .role-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }

  .role-cell {
    padding: 18px 20px;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(42,45,62,0.55);
  }

  .role-cell:last-child { border-right: none; }

  .role-cell.label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .role-cell.biblical { color: var(--biblical-blue-light); background: rgba(30,58,107,0.05); }
  .role-cell.islamic { color: var(--islamic-green-light); background: rgba(45,110,78,0.05); }
  .role-cell.note { color: var(--text-dim); }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .orientation-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .role-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .role-cell { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(42,45,62,0.35); }
    .role-cell:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  }

  /* ── VERSE TABLES ──────────────────────── */
  .verse-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .verse-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .three-cols { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
  }

  .verse-column {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 2px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .verse-col-header {
    padding: 20px 24px;
    font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .verse-col-header.islamic {
    background: rgba(45, 110, 78, 0.25);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--islamic-green);
    color: var(--islamic-green-light);
  }

  .verse-col-header.biblical {
    background: rgba(30, 58, 107, 0.25);
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--biblical-blue);
    color: var(--biblical-blue-light);
  }

  .verse-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .verse-table th {
    background: var(--surface);
    padding: 12px 16px;
    text-align: left;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .verse-table td {
    padding: 16px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(42,45,62,0.5);
    vertical-align: top;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .verse-table tr:last-child td {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .verse-table tr:hover td {
    background: rgba(201,168,76,0.03);
  }

  .verse-ref {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--gold-dim);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .verse-arabic {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--islamic-green-light);
    direction: rtl;
    line-height: 1.8;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  /* ── COMPARISON TABLE ──────────────────── */
  .compare-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 15px;
    margin-top: 30px;
  }

  .compare-table th {
    padding: 16px 20px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-align: left;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
  }

  .compare-table th:nth-child(1) { color: var(--text-dim); }
  .compare-table th:nth-child(2) { color: var(--islamic-green-light); background: rgba(45,110,78,0.1); }
  .compare-table th:nth-child(3) { color: var(--biblical-blue-light); background: rgba(30,58,107,0.1); }
  .compare-table th:nth-child(4) { color: var(--gold); background: rgba(201,168,76,0.07); }

  .compare-table td {
    padding: 16px 20px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(42,45,62,0.4);
    vertical-align: top;
  }

  .compare-table td:nth-child(2) { background: rgba(45,110,78,0.04); }
  .compare-table td:nth-child(3) { background: rgba(30,58,107,0.04); }
  .compare-table td:nth-child(4) { background: rgba(201,168,76,0.04); }

  .compare-table tr:hover td { filter: brightness(1.2); }

  .trait-label {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .match-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 3px 10px;
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    border-radius: 2px;
    margin-top: 6px;
  }

  .match-strong { background: rgba(76,201,122,0.15); color: var(--agree); border: 1px solid rgba(76,201,122,0.3); }
  .match-partial { background: rgba(201,168,76,0.15); color: var(--gold); border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3); }
  .match-inverse { background: rgba(201,76,76,0.15); color: var(--danger); border: 1px solid rgba(201,76,76,0.3); }

  /* ── THREE LENS ANALYSIS ───────────────── */
  .three-cols {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .lens-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 30px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .lens-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 3px;
  }

  .lens-card.theologian::before { background: var(--biblical-blue-light); }
  .lens-card.islamic-scholar::before { background: var(--islamic-green-light); }
  .lens-card.secular::before { background: var(--secular-purple-light); }

  .lens-icon { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px; }

  .lens-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif;
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .lens-card.theologian h3 { color: var(--biblical-blue-light); }
  .lens-card.islamic-scholar h3 { color: var(--islamic-green-light); }
  .lens-card.secular h3 { color: var(--secular-purple-light); }

  .lens-card p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .verdict-line {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 16px;
    padding-top: 16px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  .verdict-dot {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  /* ── CONCLUSION ────────────────────────── */
  .conclusion-box {
    border: 1px solid var(--gold-dim);
    padding: 50px;
    position: relative;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(201,168,76,0.05) 0%, transparent 70%);
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .conclusion-box h3 {
    font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif;
    font-size: clamp(18px, 2.5vw, 30px);
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .conclusion-box p {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 16px;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.9;
  }

  .score-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 20px;
    margin: 40px 0;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .score-card {
    padding: 20px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .score-num {
    font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif;
    font-size: 40px;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .score-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  /* ── AGENT DEBATE LOG ──────────────────── */
  .debate-log {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: var(--deep);
    padding: 0;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-top: 30px;
  }

  .debate-header {
    background: var(--surface);
    padding: 14px 20px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .status-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--agree);
    animation: blink 2s infinite;
  }

  @keyframes blink {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.3; }
  }

  .debate-entry {
    padding: 20px 24px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(42,45,62,0.4);
  }

  .agent-label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .agent-label.claude { color: #8ab4f8; }
  .agent-label.grok { color: #f08c4b; }
  .agent-label.agreed { color: var(--agree); }

  .debate-entry p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; }

  /* ── TIMELINE ──────────────────────────── */
  .timeline {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 40px;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }

  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--gold-dim), transparent);
  }

  .timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .timeline-item::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: -44px;
    top: 6px;
    width: 9px;
    height: 9px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 2px solid var(--gold);
    background: var(--obsidian);
  }

  .timeline-event {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--gold-dim);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .timeline-item h4 {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .timeline-item p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }

  /* ── REFERENCES ────────────────────────── */
  .ref-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 30px;
  }

  .ref-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 18px;
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  .ref-type {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 10px;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: var(--gold-dim);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 6px;
  }

  .ref-card h5 {
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .ref-card p { color: var(--text-dim); font-style: italic; }

  /* ── STICKY NAV ────────────────────────── */
  .sticky-nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    background: rgba(13,13,15,0.95);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 14px 40px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 24px;
    transform: translateY(-100%);
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }

  .sticky-nav.visible { transform: translateY(0); }

  .sticky-nav .brand {
    font-family: 'Cinzel Decorative', serif;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .sticky-nav a {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    text-decoration: none;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    transition: color 0.2s;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .sticky-nav a:hover { color: var(--gold); }

  /* ── CALLOUT ───────────────────────────── */
  .callout {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--gold);
    padding: 16px 20px;
    background: rgba(201,168,76,0.05);
    margin: 24px 0;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .warning-callout {
    border-left: 3px solid var(--danger);
    padding: 16px 20px;
    background: rgba(201,76,76,0.05);
    margin: 24px 0;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .warning-callout strong { color: var(--danger); }

  /* Update log */
  .update-log {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    padding: 12px 20px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 60px 40px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  footer .footer-note {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    margin-top: 10px;
    color: rgba(136,130,153,0.5);
    letter-spacing: 2px;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- STICKY NAV -->
<nav class="sticky-nav" id="stickyNav">
  <span class="brand">THE CONVERGENCE CODEX</span>
  <a href="#beginner-map">Beginner Map</a>
  <a href="#verses">Scriptures</a>
  <a href="#comparison">Comparison</a>
  <a href="#timeline">Timeline</a>
  <a href="#three-lenses">Three Lenses</a>
  <a href="#debate">Agent Debate</a>
  <a href="#conclusion">Conclusion</a>
  <a href="#references">References</a>
  <a href="#elijah-dajjal">Elijah-Dajjal?</a>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
  <div class="hero-emblem">☽✦☩</div>
  <h1>The Convergence Codex</h1>
  <div class="hero-sub">Al-Mahdi &nbsp;·&nbsp; The Antichrist &nbsp;·&nbsp; A Comparative Eschatological Study</div>

  <div class="thesis-box">
    <p>Are Islam's awaited deliverer and Christianity's end-times nemesis the same figure — seen through opposite theological lenses? This study examines every major scriptural reference, scholarly analysis, and theological argument to pursue that question with intellectual honesty.</p>
  </div>

  <nav class="nav-pills">
